## 📺 画面表示用コード

```typescript
// 加算演算子
let a: number = 10;
let b: number = 20;
let sum: number = a + b; // 30

// 実用的な例
let price: number = 1000;
let tax: number = 100;
let total: number = price + tax; // 1100

let userAge: number = 25;
let yearsToAdd: number = 5;
let futureAge: number = userAge + yearsToAdd; // 30
```